   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>This book is composed of messages concerning the course of the church given by Brother Witness Lee during a training on service in Taipei, Taiwan in 1956.</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>The general subject of this training was The Three Aspects of the Church.</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>The first aspect is the meaning of the church; the second, the course of the church; and the third, the organization of the church.</S>
   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>The messages given in this training were compiled into three books, according to the three aforementioned aspects; these books are entitled: The Meaning of the Church, The Course of the Church, and The Organization of the Church.</S>
